---
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>リスム | 空き家・古民家のリノベーション専門</title>
  <meta name="description" content="リスムは、空き家・古民家を価値ある住まいに再生するリノベーション専門サービスです。あなたの想いを形にする、丁寧なリノベーションをご提案します。" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@300;400;500;700&family=Noto+Serif+JP:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    :root {
      --color-primary: #2D6A4F;
      --color-primary-light: #52B788;
      --color-primary-dark: #1B4332;
      --color-accent: #D4A853;
      --color-bg: #FAFAF8;
      --color-text: #1A1A1A;
      --color-text-muted: #6B7280;
      --color-border: #E5E7EB;
      --font-sans: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
      --font-serif: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
    }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body { font-family: var(--font-sans); background: var(--color-bg); color: var(--color-text); line-height: 1.7; }

    /* HEADER */
    header { position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100; background: rgba(250,250,248,0.95); backdrop-filter: blur(8px); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); padding: 0 40px; height: 64px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; }
    .logo { font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: 1.5rem; color: var(--color-primary-dark); text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }
    .logo span { color: var(--color-primary-light); }
    nav { display: flex; gap: 32px; align-items: center; }
    nav a { text-decoration: none; color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 500; transition: color 0.2s; }
    nav a:hover { color: var(--color-primary); }
    .nav-cta { background: var(--color-primary); color: #fff !important; padding: 10px 24px; border-radius: 100px; font-weight: 700 !important; }
    .nav-cta:hover { background: var(--color-primary-dark) !important; }

    /* HERO */
    .hero { min-height: 100vh; padding-top: 64px; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; align-items: center; max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding-left: 60px; padding-right: 60px; gap: 60px; }
    .hero-content { padding: 80px 0; }
    .hero-badge { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; background: #E8F5E9; color: var(--color-primary); font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 700; padding: 6px 16px; border-radius: 100px; margin-bottom: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.08em; }
    .hero-badge::before { content: ''; width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--color-primary-light); }
    .hero h1 { font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.2rem); line-height: 1.4; color: var(--color-primary-dark); margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .hero h1 em { font-style: normal; color: var(--color-primary-light); }
    .hero-desc { font-size: 1rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); margin-bottom: 40px; max-width: 440px; }
    .hero-actions { display: flex; gap: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .btn-primary { background: var(--color-primary); color: #fff; padding: 16px 36px; border-radius: 100px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1rem; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; }
    .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--color-primary-dark); transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(45,106,79,0.3); }
    .btn-secondary { background: transparent; color: var(--color-primary); padding: 16px 36px; border-radius: 100px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1rem; text-decoration: none; border: 2px solid var(--color-primary); transition: all 0.2s; }
    .btn-secondary:hover { background: var(--color-primary); color: #fff; }
    .hero-visual { position: relative; height: 520px; }
    .hero-image-main { width: 100%; height: 100%; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #52B788 0%, #2D6A4F 50%, #1B4332 100%); border-radius: 24px; overflow: hidden; position: relative; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
    .hero-image-main::before { content: '🏠'; font-size: 120px; opacity: 0.3; position: absolute; bottom: 20px; right: 20px; }
    .hero-image-text { text-align: center; color: #fff; z-index: 1; }
    .hero-image-text p { font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.5; }
    .hero-image-text span { font-size: 0.9rem; opacity: 0.8; display: block; margin-top: 8px; }
    .hero-stat { position: absolute; background: #fff; border-radius: 16px; padding: 16px 20px; box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
    .hero-stat-1 { bottom: -24px; left: -24px; }
    .hero-stat-2 { top: 40px; right: -24px; }
    .hero-stat .num { font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-primary); }
    .hero-stat .label { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); }

    /* SECTION COMMON */
    section { padding: 100px 40px; }
    .section-inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .section-label { font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.15em; color: var(--color-primary-light); text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .section-title { font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 2.4rem); color: var(--color-primary-dark); margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.4; }
    .section-desc { color: var(--color-text-muted); max-width: 560px; font-size: 1rem; }
    .section-header { margin-bottom: 60px; }

    /* FEATURES */
    .features { background: #fff; }
    .features-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 32px; }
    .feature-card { padding: 40px 32px; border-radius: 20px; border: 1px solid var(--color-border); transition: all 0.3s; background: var(--color-bg); }
    .feature-card:hover { transform: translateY(-6px); box-shadow: 0 16px 48px rgba(45,106,79,0.12); border-color: var(--color-primary-light); }
    .feature-icon { font-size: 2.4rem; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .feature-title { font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: 1.2rem; color: var(--color-primary-dark); margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .feature-desc { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); line-height: 1.8; }

    /* PROCESS */
    .process { background: var(--color-bg); }
    .process-steps { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 24px; position: relative; }
    .process-steps::before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: 40px; left: 60px; right: 60px; height: 2px; background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--color-primary-light), var(--color-primary)); z-index: 0; }
    .process-step { text-align: center; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
    .process-num { width: 80px; height: 80px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--color-primary); color: #fff; font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin: 0 auto 24px; box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(45,106,79,0.3); }
    .process-step-title { font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-primary-dark); margin-bottom: 8px; font-size: 1rem; }
    .process-step-desc { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); line-height: 1.7; }

    /* CASES */
    .cases { background: #fff; }
    .cases-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 28px; }
    .case-card { border-radius: 20px; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid var(--color-border); transition: all 0.3s; background: var(--color-bg); }
    .case-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
    .case-img { height: 200px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 4rem; }
    .case-img-1 { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #B7E4C7, #52B788); }
    .case-img-2 { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #D4A853, #A97C2B); }
    .case-img-3 { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #74C69D, #2D6A4F); }
    .case-body { padding: 24px; }
    .case-tag { display: inline-block; background: #E8F5E9; color: var(--color-primary); font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700; padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 100px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .case-title { font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--color-primary-dark); margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .case-desc { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .case-meta { display: flex; gap: 16px; font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); }
    .case-meta strong { color: var(--color-primary); }

    /* VOICE */
    .voice { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1B4332 0%, #2D6A4F 100%); }
    .voice .section-title { color: #fff; }
    .voice .section-label { color: var(--color-primary-light); }
    .voice .section-desc { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); }
    .voice-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 24px; }
    .voice-card { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); backdrop-filter: blur(10px); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15); border-radius: 20px; padding: 32px; }
    .voice-stars { color: var(--color-accent); font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .voice-text { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 24px; font-style: italic; }
    .voice-author { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; }
    .voice-avatar { width: 44px; height: 44px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--color-primary-light); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 1.2rem; }
    .voice-name { color: #fff; font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.9rem; }
    .voice-info { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); font-size: 0.8rem; }

    /* CTA */
    .cta { background: var(--color-bg); text-align: center; }
    .cta-box { background: #fff; border-radius: 32px; padding: 80px 60px; border: 2px solid var(--color-border); max-width: 780px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .cta-box .section-title { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .cta-box .section-desc { text-align: center; margin: 0 auto 40px; }
    .cta-actions { display: flex; gap: 16px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .cta-note { margin-top: 20px; font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); }

    /* FAQ */
    .faq { background: #fff; }
    .faq-list { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .faq-item { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); padding: 28px 0; }
    .faq-q { font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-primary-dark); font-size: 1rem; margin-bottom: 12px; display: flex; gap: 12px; align-items: flex-start; }
    .faq-q::before { content: 'Q'; background: var(--color-primary); color: #fff; width: 24px; height: 24px; border-radius: 6px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 0.85rem; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .faq-a { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); line-height: 1.8; padding-left: 36px; }

    /* FOOTER */
    footer { background: var(--color-primary-dark); color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); padding: 60px 40px 40px; }
    .footer-inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .footer-top { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 48px; padding-bottom: 48px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); margin-bottom: 40px; }
    .footer-logo { font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: 1.8rem; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .footer-logo span { color: var(--color-primary-light); }
    .footer-about { font-size: 0.85rem; line-height: 1.8; }
    .footer-nav h4 { color: #fff; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.08em; }
    .footer-nav ul { list-style: none; }
    .footer-nav li { margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .footer-nav a { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.85rem; transition: color 0.2s; }
    .footer-nav a:hover { color: var(--color-primary-light); }
    .footer-bottom { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; font-size: 0.8rem; }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      header { padding: 0 20px; }
      nav { display: none; }
      .hero { grid-template-columns: 1fr; padding: 100px 24px 60px; gap: 40px; }
      .hero-visual { height: 280px; }
      section { padding: 60px 24px; }
      .features-grid, .cases-grid, .voice-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .process-steps { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
      .process-steps::before { display: none; }
      .footer-top { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 32px; }
      .footer-bottom { flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; text-align: center; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <a href="#" class="logo">リ<span>ス</span>ム</a>
    <nav>
      <a href="#features">特長</a>
      <a href="#process">流れ</a>
      <a href="#cases">実績</a>
      <a href="#faq">FAQ</a>
      <a href="#contact" class="nav-cta">無料相談</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <div class="hero">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <div class="hero-badge">空き家・古民家リノベーション専門</div>
      <h1>眠っている家に、<br /><em>新しい命</em>を吹き込む</h1>
      <p class="hero-desc">リスムは、空き家・古民家を価値ある住まいに再生するリノベーション専門サービスです。地域に根ざした丁寧な提案で、あなたの想いを形にします。</p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="#contact" class="btn-primary">無料相談を予約する →</a>
        <a href="#cases" class="btn-secondary">施工事例を見る</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-visual">
      <div class="hero-image-main">
        <div class="hero-image-text">
          <p>空き家を<br />宝に変える</p>
          <span>Reform × Resume = RISUM</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-stat hero-stat-1">
        <div class="num">150+</div>
        <div class="label">累計施工実績</div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-stat hero-stat-2">
        <div class="num">98%</div>
        <div class="label">顧客満足度</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="features" id="features">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div class="section-label">Features</div>
        <h2 class="section-title">リスムが選ばれる3つの理由</h2>
        <p class="section-desc">空き家・古民家のリノベーションに特化したプロフェッショナルチームが、ワンストップでサポートします。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">🏡</div>
          <h3 class="feature-title">古民家・空き家に特化</h3>
          <p class="feature-desc">一般的なリフォーム会社では断られがちな古民家・空き家も、豊富な経験と専門知識でしっかり対応。構造診断から竣工まで一貫してサポートします。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">💬</div>
          <h3 class="feature-title">ワンストップ相談窓口</h3>
          <p class="feature-desc">設計・施工・資金調達・補助金申請まで、窓口はリスム一本。複数業者への連絡や調整の手間を省き、スムーズな進行を実現します。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">🌿</div>
          <h3 class="feature-title">地域素材×現代デザイン</h3>
          <p class="feature-desc">地元の木材や職人技を活かしながら、現代の暮らしに合ったデザインに再生。その土地の魅力を引き出した、唯一無二の住まいをご提案します。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="process" id="process">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div class="section-label">Process</div>
        <h2 class="section-title">ご相談から完成まで</h2>
        <p class="section-desc">はじめての方でも安心。4つのステップで、理想の住まいへ。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="process-steps">
        <div class="process-step">
          <div class="process-num">01</div>
          <div class="process-step-title">無料相談</div>
          <p class="process-step-desc">物件の状態やご要望をヒアリング。オンラインでも対応可能です。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="process-step">
          <div class="process-num">02</div>
          <div class="process-step-title">現地調査・診断</div>
          <p class="process-step-desc">専門家が物件を詳しく調査。構造・設備・劣化状況を確認します。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="process-step">
          <div class="process-num">03</div>
          <div class="process-step-title">プラン・お見積り</div>
          <p class="process-step-desc">ご要望と予算に合わせたプランをご提案。補助金活用もご案内します。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="process-step">
          <div class="process-num">04</div>
          <div class="process-step-title">施工・お引渡し</div>
          <p class="process-step-desc">丁寧な施工と定期報告で安心。完成後のアフターサポートも充実。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cases" id="cases">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div class="section-label">Cases</div>
        <h2 class="section-title">施工事例</h2>
        <p class="section-desc">実際にリスムが手がけた空き家・古民家の再生事例をご紹介します。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="cases-grid">
        <div class="case-card">
          <div class="case-img case-img-1">🏠</div>
          <div class="case-body">
            <span class="case-tag">古民家リノベ</span>
            <h3 class="case-title">築80年の古民家を家族の拠点に再生</h3>
            <p class="case-desc">梁や柱を活かしながら、断熱・耐震性能を現代水準に。週末移住拠点として活用中。</p>
            <div class="case-meta">
              <span>工期: <strong>4ヶ月</strong></span>
              <span>予算: <strong>800万円台</strong></span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="case-card">
          <div class="case-img case-img-2">🏡</div>
          <div class="case-body">
            <span class="case-tag">空き家活用</span>
            <h3 class="case-title">10年空き家を民泊施設へ転換</h3>
            <p class="case-desc">補助金を最大活用し、総費用を大幅圧縮。開業から半年でコスト回収の見通しも。</p>
            <div class="case-meta">
              <span>工期: <strong>3ヶ月</strong></span>
              <span>予算: <strong>500万円台</strong></span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="case-card">
          <div class="case-img case-img-3">🌿</div>
          <div class="case-body">
            <span class="case-tag">フルリノベ</span>
            <h3 class="case-title">築50年の実家を二世帯住宅にリノベ</h3>
            <p class="case-desc">親世帯・子世帯それぞれのプライバシーを確保しながら、つながりを感じる設計に。</p>
            <div class="case-meta">
              <span>工期: <strong>5ヶ月</strong></span>
              <span>予算: <strong>1,200万円台</strong></span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="voice">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div class="section-label">Voice</div>
        <h2 class="section-title">お客様の声</h2>
        <p class="section-desc">リスムを選んでいただいたお客様からのリアルな声をご紹介します。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="voice-grid">
        <div class="voice-card">
          <div class="voice-stars">★★★★★</div>
          <p class="voice-text">「他社では難しいと断られた古民家でしたが、リスムさんは可能性を見出してくれました。完成した住まいは想像以上で、毎日が楽しいです。」</p>
          <div class="voice-author">
            <div class="voice-avatar">👨</div>
            <div>
              <div class="voice-name">田中 健二さん</div>
              <div class="voice-info">40代・兵庫県 / 古民家リノベ</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="voice-card">
          <div class="voice-stars">★★★★★</div>
          <p class="voice-text">「補助金の申請もすべてお任せできて助かりました。費用が想定より大幅に抑えられ、使いやすい民泊施設が完成しました。」</p>
          <div class="voice-author">
            <div class="voice-avatar">👩</div>
            <div>
              <div class="voice-name">山田 裕子さん</div>
              <div class="voice-info">50代・京都府 / 空き家活用</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="voice-card">
          <div class="voice-stars">★★★★★</div>
          <p class="voice-text">「担当の方が毎週進捗を報告してくれたので安心でした。遠方に住んでいても実家の改修をスムーズに進めることができました。」</p>
